snippet.title: The Classroom (2003) Perfect Stealth Walkthrough
snippet.description:
Always glad to play a stealth game with more level variety than Phantom Pain!

The April Fools joke is that I scheduled and recorded this ahead of time so I'm still technically on hiatus.
